<br>
If he is prepared, golem his Circles off of him, or your rains won't do alot..<br>
<br>
It forces him to move mid heal ..or outdamages the heals..the best is the 59 tears of prexus.  I had a 60 cleric decide to nuke me last night..as he started to cast, I had already started my rain..his Magic based spell was absorbed by my spellshield, after 1 rain, 1 lure..he was dead. <br>
<br>
This works well for most healing classes..they will try to stand next to you if smart.  Keep an eye out for the cast message, stop running, hit a rain spell or an interupt.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ullyapakadeabn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llyap aka Deabn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/13/02 3:55:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=64.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> well</span><hr size=1> I am only 33, but so far 20pp pumice&gt;druid dots.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udarkudaos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>darkudaos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/27/02 3:11:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=64.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: well</span><hr size=1> Golem wand/pumice the little tree hugger till he falls from the sky (soe), then watch him panic as he tries to heal, mem, recast soe and get out of range all at once. have all resists up, dispell ro's and WD as they land, have 2 open slots and 2 junk buffs below them, (in case you are dispelled first off) if only dot/debuff is on you chuck a click buff up and pumice/dispell self, so that you dont eat into your real buffs. They can't dot you to death if you pumice fast, and they cant nuke you to death if you pumice fast. But unless you are prepared (sow included) and near to FM (will need it to outlast the heals), gate. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20%